                    <span>Steven Van Yoder's book is tied along with Robert Bly's "Become A Recognized Authority In Your Field - In 60 Days Or Less" as one of the two best books available on personal branding.  In addition to these two books, I'd also like to point you toward C.J. Hayden's wonderful "Get Clients Now."  Any of these books is ideal for service professionals trying to build a brand and a reputation.  Consultants, in particular, will benefit from studying these three books.  Highly recommended.</span>
                  
              
